Package: functiondepends
Type: Package
Title: Find functions and their dependencies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Jakub",
    "Sobolewski",
    email = "jakupsob@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The purpose of this package is to find functions in unstructured directory
     and to find dependencies between user-defined functions found in given directory.
     Sourcing of R files is performed without side-effects i.e. from R scripts that have
     executable code and function definitions only function definitions will be evaluated.
